Sure, here are some example sentences in Serbian using the word "borac" in different forms and positions:

1. On je *borac* za ljudska prava. (He is a *fighter* for human rights.)
2. Naš klub će se takmičiti sa najboljim *borcima* u regionu. (Our club will compete with the best *fighters* in the region.)
3. *Borci* su pokazali hrabrost u bici. (*Fighters* showed courage in battle.)
4. Trening *boraca* počinje u 17 sati. (Fighter training starts at 5 pm.)
5. Svaki *borac* mora imati dobru kondiciju. (Every *fighter* must have good physical fitness.)
6. *Borac* je bio zadovoljan nakon pobede. (*The fighter* was satisfied after the victory.)
7. *Borci* iz različitih država su se okupili na ovom takmičenju. (*Fighters* from different countries gathered at this competition.)
8. Ovaj film govori o mladom *borcu* koji se bori sa bolešću. (This movie is about a young *fighter* who is battling illness.)
9. Svi učesnici turnira su pokazali svoje sposobnosti kao *borci*. (All tournament participants demonstrated their abilities as *fighters*.)
10. *Borac* je pobedio svog protivnika nokautom. (*The fighter* defeated his opponent by knockout.)

I hope these examples help!